  "title": "Brewing Guide",
  "description": "No clue how to brew a potion?\nThis pack brings the solution by intoducing a fitting Brewing Guide into the game!",
  "body": "\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2IKKnuE.png\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" border=\"0\"/>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/hM7UhuRFaa\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7e84ea1620a5fb574fc32bdda57ca8319c3a29dc.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" border=\"10\"/>\n    </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/kingybu\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/877ebfd2654ffc553f963d6871513d935b3c741f.png\" width=\"220\" height=\"220\" border=\"10\"/>\n    </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kingybusiness/\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1bb902bda9644d160934a49c82aa5377c21fc04e.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"200\" border=\"10\"/>\n            </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    Tired of searching the internet every time you have to brew a potion? Well, be no more! Brewing Guide is a texture pack that aims to bring a crafting book-type system to Minecraft without ruining the Vanilla feel.<br><br>\n    This Resource-Pack is a remake of \n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/in-game-brewing-guide\">In-Game Brewing Guide</a> \n    by \n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/PINPAL\">THE_PINPAL</a>.\n</p>\n\n![Preview](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/76c68b60a07df5e6d9f43e5b9e6513f8b789893d.png)\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5f7fe74c90e1c2c59cc969e12bd49d2220ade505.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" border=\"0\"/>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <strong>THE_PINPAL & Kingybu</strong>\n</p>\n",
